<br>
Sony has recently added a new link for upcoming changes to their website. This is taken from <!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://eqlive.station.sony.com/updates/upcoming_updates.jsp">eqlive.station.sony.com/u...pdates.jsp</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br>
